  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a donabe vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until it is lightly browned.",
    "Add the garlic, ground cumin, ground coriander, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb and cook until it is browned on all sides.",
    "Add the reduced ginger cordial and yogurt, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook, covered, until the lamb is tender.",
    "Serve the rogan josh hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for an additional 10 minutes."
